# Changelog

All notable changes to the Quami project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.1.0] - 2025-10-20

### Added

- Initial release of Quami - 3D interactive AI companion application
- Integration with Kwami v2.0.0 as git submodule
- 3D interactive blob visualization with real-time morphing
- Audio-reactive animations with multiple skin options (tricolor, zebra)
- Voice interaction capabilities with speech-to-text and text-to-speech
- Natural language AI conversation system
- User authentication via Supabase (email and wallet)
- Wallet integration with Solana blockchain
- Multi-language support (English, French, Spanish) via i18n
- Profile management and session persistence
- Dark mode and theme customization
- Responsive UI with Nuxt UI components
- Server-side API routes for backend functionality

### Architecture

- Built on Nuxt.js 4 with SSR disabled for optimal client-side performance
- Kwami library integrated as git submodule at `app/@kwami/`
- State management with Pinia and persisted state support
- Three.js for 3D graphics rendering
- Supabase for backend services and authentication
- TypeScript for type safety across the application

### Technical Details

- Node server preset for production builds
- Vite-based development environment
- ESLint configuration with stylistic rules
- Optimized dependency bundling for Web3 libraries
- CORS-enabled API routes for external integrations
- View transitions for smooth page navigation
